hadiths[38]{hadithnumber,text}:
3162,"Hazrat Umme Kurz (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna , aap farma rahey they : ladkey ki taraf sey do eik jaisi bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri (Aqiqa key tor par zibeh ki jaey.)"
3163,"Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamen hukm diya ke hum ladkey ki taraf sey do bakriyan aur ladki ki taraf sey eik bakri Aqiqey key tor par zibeh karen."
3164,"Hazrat Salman bin Aamir (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai unhoney Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey suna, aap farma rahey they : bachey key sath Aqiqa hai, chunaanche uski taraf sey khoon bahao aur uska mail kuchail door karo ."
3165,"Hazrat Samra (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : har ladka apney aqeeqe key badley girwi hai. saatwen din uski taraf sey (aqeeqe ka janwer) zibeh kya jaey aur uskey sar key baal utarey jaeyn aur uska naam rakha jaey ."
3166,"Hazrat Yazeed bin abd Muzni sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ladkey ki taraf sey Aqiqa kya jaey, aur uskey sar ko khoon na lagaya jaey."
3167,"Hazrat Nabisha (bin Abdullah Hazli) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aadmi ney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ko aawaz dey kar (apni taraf mutawajjeh kya aur) kaha : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum zamana jahiliyat mein rajab key mahiney mein Ateera zibeh kya kartey they. ab aap hamen kya hukm farmatey hain? Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah key naam par zibeh karo, chahey kisi mahiney mein ho. aur Allah (ki raza) key liye neki karo aur khana khilao. haazirin ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum jahiliyat mein faraa key naam sey janwer zibeh kartey they. ab hamen aap ka kya hukm hai? farmaya : har charney waley janweron (key rewad) mein faraa (mashroo) hai, jo terey maweshi sey paida ho yahan tak key jab wo bojh uthaney (ya jufti) key qabil ho jaey to to usey zibeh kar key uska gosht musafiron par sadqa kar dey , yehi baat behtar hai."
3168,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi Faraa nahin aur koi Ateera nahin. (Imam Ibne-Maja key ustaad) Hazrat Hisham bin Ammar (Rahimahullah) bayan kartey hain : Faraa (janwer ka) pehla bacha hota tha aur Ateera us bakri ko kehtey they jo ghar waley rajab mein zibeh kartey they."
3169,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : koi Faraa nahin aur koi Ateera nahin. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney farmaya : ye hadees Adni ki Naadir hadeeson mein sey hai."
3170,"Hazrat Shaddad bin Aus (bin Sabit) (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : Allah azz-w-jall ney har chiz par ehsan karna farz kya hai, lihaza jab tum qatl karo to achey andaz sey qatl karo aur jab tum zibeh karo to achey andaz sey zibeh karo . aadmi ko chahiye ke apni chhuri tez karey aur zibeh honey waley janwer ko aaram pahunchaey."
3171,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik aadmi key paas sey guzrey jo eik bakri ko kaan sey pakad kar kheenchey liye ja raha tha. aap ney farmaya : uska kaan chhod dey. gardan sey pakad ley .
3172,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney chhuri ko tez karney aur janweron sey chupa kar rakhney ka hukm diya . aur farmaya : jab tum mein sey koi shakhs zibeh karey to jaldi sey zibeh kar daley. Imam Ibne-Maja (Rahimahullah) ney mazkura riwayat eik dusri sanad sey bhi Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey isi tarah bayan ki hai."
3173,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai ke (unhoney ye aayat padhi) : ( وإِنَّ الشَّيَاطِينَ , لَيُوحُونَ إِلَى أَوْلِيَائِهِمْ )' beshak shetan apney doston ki taraf ilhaam kartey hain. (phir uski wazahat kartey huye) farmaya : (mushrik) log kehtey they : jis chiz par Allah ka naam liya jaey wo na khao, aur jis par Allah ka naam na liya jaey, wo kha liya karo. Allah Taala ney (un ki tardeed mein) ye aayat nazil farma di ( وَلَا تَأْكُلُوا مِمَّا لَمْ يُذْكَرِ اسْمُ اللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ )' jis chiz par Allah ka naam na liya jaey is mein sey (kuch) na khao ."
3174,"ummul-mominin sayeda Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai ke baaz afrad ney arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! kuch log hamarey paas gosht ley kar aatey hain, hamen malum nahin hota ke (zibeh karey waqt) is par Allah ka naam liya gaya hai ya nahin (to hum kya keren?) aap ney farmaya : tum Allah ka naam ley lo aur kha lo . ye log naey-naey kufr sey Islam mein dakhil huye they."
3175,"Hazrat Muhammad bin Sefi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : mainey do khargosh pathar sey zibeh kiye aur unhen ley kar Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir ho gaya to aap ney mujhey unko kha leney ka hukm diya."
3176,Hazrat Zaid bin Sabit (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke kisi bhediye ney eik bakri mein daant gaad diye (aur usey zakhmi kar diya) to malikon ney isey pathar sey zibeh kar liya. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen usey kha leney ki ijazat dey di.
3177,"Hazrat Adi bin Hatim Taai (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke unhoney kaha : mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool! hum log shikar kartey hain (baaz oqaat) hamen (zibeh karney key liye) tez pathar ya dandey ki khinchi key siwa kuchh nahin milta. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz key sath chaho khoon baha lo, aur is par (zibeh kartey waqt) Allah ka naam ley lo ."
3178,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum log Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath eik safar mein they. mainey arz kya : aey Allah key Rasool ! hum jangon mein jatey hain aur (maal ghanimat mein milney waley janwer zibeh karney key liye) hamarey paas chhuriyaan nahin hotin. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz key sath khoon jari ho jaey, aur is par Allah ka naam liya jaey to (is tarah zibeh kiye huye janwer ka gosht) kha ley, siwaye daant aur nakhun key kyonkey daant to haddi hai aur nakhun habshiyon ki chhuriyaan hain."
3179,"Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik ladkey key paas sey guzrey jo eik bakri ki khaal utaar raha tha. Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney usey farmaya : eik taraf ho ja , main tujhey (khaal utaarna) sikhata hun . Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney apna haath khaal aur gosht key darmiyan rakha aur usey zor sey dakhil farmaya yahan tak key baghal tak bazu chup gaya . farmaya : ladkey ! is tarah khaal utaar. phir aap chal diye aur (ja kar) logon ko namaz padhaai aur (namaz key liye naya) wuzu nahin kya."
3180,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) eik Ansari Sabab key yahan tashrif ley gaey . usney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key liye janwer zibeh karney key iraday sey chhuri pakdi to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney us sey farmaya : doodh deney wala janwer zibeh karney sey ijtinab karna."
3181,"Hazrat abu-Bakar bin abu-Qahafa (Raziallahu anha) (Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key khalifa) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen aur Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey farmaya : chalo (Hurmi bin Abdullah bin Rifaa (Waqifii) Ansari (Raziallahu anhu)) key yahan chalen. hum chaand ki chaandni mein chal kar) unkey (baagh mein pahunchey. unhoney khush aamadeed kaha, phir chhuri ley kar bakriyon mein chakkar lagaya (taake munasib bakri dekh kar zibeh ki jaey.) Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : doodh deney wali (ko zibeh kerney) sey perhez karna."
3182,Hazrat Kaab bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke eik aurat ney pathar key sath bakri zibeh kar li. ye baat Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ki khidmat mein arz ki gaee to aap ney is mein koi harj nahin samjha.
3183,"Hazrat Raafey bin khadij (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : eik safar mein hum log Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they ke eik oont bhag nikla. eik aadmi ney is par teer chala diya. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : un (maweshiyon) mein kuch bhag nikalney waley hotey hain jis tarah jangli janwer (insan sey door) bhagtey hain, lihaza un mein sey jo tum par ghalib aa jaey (qabu na aaye) uskey sath isi tarah kya karo ."
3184,"Hazrat Abul-Ushra (Usama bin Malik) (Rahimahullah) apney walid ( Malik bin Qahtam) sey riwayat kartey hain ke unhoney farmaya : aey Allah key Rasool ! kya zibeh sirf halaq aur gardan hi sey hota hai? aap ney farmaya : agar to uski raan mein neza maar dey , tab bhi kafi hoga ."
3185,Hazrat abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney janweron ka musla karney sey mana farmaya hai.
3186,"Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ( nishana bazi key liye) janwer ko baandhney sey mana farmaya."
3187,"Hazrat Abdullah bin Abbas (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : jis chiz mein rooh mojud ho, usey (mashq key liye teeron waghera ka) nishana na banao ."
3188,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Allah key Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney is baat sey mana farmaya ke kisi janwer ko baandh kar qatl kya jaey ."
3189,"Hazrat Abdullah bin umr (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney gandagi khaney waley janwer key gosht aur doodh sey mana farmaya."
3190,"Hazrat Asma bint abi Bakar (Raziallahu anha) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key zamaney mein hamney apna ghoda zibeh kar key uska gosht khaya ."
3191,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney ghazwa khaibar key zamaney mein ghodon aur jangli gadhon ka gosht khaya ."
3192,"Hazrat Abu-Is'haq (Suleman bin abi Suleman) Shebani Rahimahullah sey riwayat hai, unhoney bayan kya : mainey Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey paaltu gadhon key gosht key barey mein sawal kya to unhoney farmaya : jang khaibar key moqey par jab hum Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath they, hamen (khurak ki qillat ki wajeh sey) bhook ka samna karna pada. sathiyon ko shehar sey bahar kuch gadhey haath lag gaey. hamney unhen zibeh kar liya . hamari degen ubal rahi thin ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key manadi ney aelan kar diya : degen ulta do aur gadhon ka gosht bilkul na khao , chunanche hamney wo ( degen) ulat din. Abu-Is'haq (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain : hamney Hazrat Abdullah bin abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen bilkul haram kar diya? unhoney farmaya : hum log (Sahaba kiraam) ye baaten kartey they ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney unhen qatae tor par haram kar diya kyonkey wo gandagi khatey hain."
3193,Hazrat Miqdam bin Madi karb kandi (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney bahut-si cheezon ki hurmat bayan farmaai yahan tak key paaltu gadhon ka bhi zikr farmaya.
3194,"Hazrat Bara bin Aazib (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney hamein paaltu gadhon ka kachcha aur pakka huwa (dono tarah ka) gosht phenk deney ka hukm diya, phir uskey baad (kabhi) us (ko khaney) ka hukm nahin diya."
3195,"Hazrat Salma bin Akwaa (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key sath khaibar ki jang ladi . Sham ko logon ney (jagah jagah) aag roshan ki. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : tum kis chiz (ko pakaaney) key liye aag jala rahey ho? Sahaba ney arz kya : paaltu gadhon key gosht key liye . aap ney farmaya : un (bartanon) mein jo kuch hai gira do, aur un (bartanon) ko tod do. eik aadmi ney kaha : ya ( agar aap ijazat den to) hum unkey andar jo kuch hai gira den aur un bartanon ko dho lein? to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : ya aisey kar lo."
3196,Hazrat Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) key aelan karney waley ney aelan kya : Allah Taala aur uska Rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) tumhen paaltu gadhon key gosht (key khaney) sey mana kartey hain kyonkey wo napak hai.
3197,"Hazrat Jabir bin Abdullah (Raziallahu anhuma) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hum ghodon ka gosht khaya kartey they. (Ata (Rahimahullah) farmatey hain :) mainey kaha : khachcharon ka ( kya hukm hai ?) unhoney farmaya : nahin (hum unka gosht nahin khatey they.)"
3198,"Hazrat Khalid bin Waleed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney ghodon, khachcharon aur gadhon ka gosht khaney sey mana farmaya."
3199,"Hazrat abu-Saeed (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai, unhoney farmaya : hamney Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) sey) zibeh honey waley mada janwer key (pet key bachey key barey mein sawal kya to Rasoolullah (Sallallahu Alehi w Aalehi Wasallam) ney farmaya : agar chaho to usey kha lo kyonkey uska zibeh uski maa ka zibeh hona hi hai. Imam abu-Adbullah (Ibne-Maja) kehtey hain : mainey Kosaj Is-haq bin Mansoor ko zibeh key mutalliq kehtey huye suna : (jo maa key zibeh karney sey pet key bachey key zabah honey key qaail nahin hain unka kehna hai) maa key zibeh honey sey janeen key zibeh honey ka haq ada nahin hota.) Is-haq ney (kaha Mazamma, Zamam aur Mazamma sey yani mazkura ibarat mein) lafz Mazamma haq o hurmat key maana mein hai na ke mazammat key maana mein."
